name: Lucy "the joyful" Enigma
description:
as a response/tribute to Asteraspace's Lucy Enigma music video that has just released recently, and as the designer of the character this artwork is made to illustrate who Lucy is. 

And with this illustration i'm opening a door to a potential of making more character illustration piece, and personification of other artist i know and adore as a friend.
this will be the first.
